{"tid":455921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"慢熱？我屌爆你老母呀","createTime":"2017-11-02T13:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T18:18:24.000Z","uid":116968,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b13503be83d2c5fdc946af9b12c8e2d3c15aca","tid":455921,"uid":116968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"一個人如果真係鐘意你，點會捨得冷落你。<br />\n佢點會捨得要你等佢。<br />\n佢唔係慢熱。佢只係唔想對住你熱。<br />\n因為人地冇鐘意過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常男仔有個女仔表白只要對方唔係咁唔掂嘅都會接受先。<br />\n姐係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有得食食左先呀！乜撚嘢日子越耐就越愛你呀！收嗲啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢真係愛你，佢一定會拎出勇氣去主動。<br />\n冇主動。咪姐係人地唔撚鐘意你。唔想對住你主動呀！<br />\n幾慢熱都好，見到心動嘅人都會豁出去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒未呀！屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"b760b56832ac82dd997371af186fa204e214b14d","tid":455921,"uid":28800,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45b499de122a8d6dfae576eced2d6d6f9cdcd533","tid":455921,"uid":116968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都同一種諗法咩<br />\n慢熱就係慢熱架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔明想點"},{"pid":"f69dabcd2d7dbc3e9346505684a7427e88ad931f","tid":455921,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"慢熱都唔撚得 抵撚你上黎叫春啦屌你老母個閪"},{"pid":"fe129c9ba277bde60b9d0623ba5f5beae94a8815","tid":455921,"uid":116968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"唉屌你 我唔撚想掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63640cbd9b3c79f5f6daa70727dac0ebc69273cb","tid":455921,"uid":99302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"因為越諗就覺得自己越配唔上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 